{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 📡 stream_mode: `updates` vs `values`\n",
    "\n",
    "> `updates` = 只看每个 node 刚刚返回了什么（delta）\n",
    ">\n",
    "> `values` = 看每一步之后完整 state 变成了什么（snapshot）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 1️⃣ `stream_mode=\"updates\"`\n",
    "\n",
    "输出的是 **node 的返回值 delta**。\n",
    "\n",
    "你的 graph 里 node 叫 `conversation`，所以输出长这样：\n",
    "\n",
    "```python\n",
    "{\n",
    "    \"conversation\": {\n",
    "        \"messages\": [AIMessage(...)]\n",
    "    }\n",
    "}\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "意思：conversation 这个 node 刚刚返回了 `{\"messages\": [AIMessage(...)]}`\n",
    "\n",
    "- 它 **不是完整 state**\n",
    "- 它只是告诉你：这个 node 这一步更新了什么"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 使用 updates 模式\n",
    "# for chunk in graph.stream(..., stream_mode=\"updates\"):\n",
    "#     for msg in chunk[\"conversation\"][\"messages\"]:\n",
    "#         msg.pretty_print()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "这时只会打印 AI 回复，因为这个 node 只返回了 AIMessage。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 2️⃣ `stream_mode=\"values\"`\n",
    "\n",
    "输出的是 **每一步之后的完整 state**。\n",
    "\n",
    "第一次看到：\n",
    "```text\n",
    "Human: hi! I'm Lance\n",
    "```\n",
    "（刚把输入放进 state 后的状态）\n",
    "\n",
    "然后 node 执行完以后，state 变成：\n",
    "```text\n",
    "Human: hi! I'm Lance\n",
    "AI: Hello, Lance! ...\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "⚠️ `values` 会看起来"重复打印 HumanMessage"，但不是重复生成，而是因为每次打印的是 **完整 state**。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 📊 对比示例\n",
    "\n",
    "假设：\n",
    "- 初始输入：`messages = [HumanMessage(\"hi\")]`\n",
    "- `conversation` node 返回：`{\"messages\": [AIMessage(\"hello\")]}`\n",
    "- 最终 state：`{\"messages\": [HumanMessage(\"hi\"), AIMessage(\"hello\")]}`\n",
    "\n",
    "### `updates` 看到的：\n",
    "\n",
    "```python\n",
    "{\n",
    "    \"conversation\": {\n",
    "        \"messages\": [AIMessage(\"hello\")]\n",
    "    }\n",
    "}\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "### `values` 看到的：\n",
    "\n",
    "**第一次：**\n",
    "```python\n",
    "{\"messages\": [HumanMessage(\"hi\")]}\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "**第二次：**\n",
    "```python\n",
    "{\"messages\": [HumanMessage(\"hi\"), AIMessage(\"hello\")]}\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 💡 一句话总结\n",
    "\n",
    "> `updates` 适合看 **每个 node 输出了什么**（delta）\n",
    ">\n",
    "> `values` 适合看 **整个 state 现在是什么样子**（snapshot）\n",
    "\n",
    "| 模式 | 看到什么 | 适合场景 |\n",
    "|------|------|------|\n",
    "| `updates` | node 的返回值 | 调试单个 node 的行为 |\n",
    "| `values` | 完整 state | 观察 state 如何演变 |"
   ]
  }
 ],
